race.comment: COSMO CENTAURUS (6) was in the betting when resuming and didn't let supporters down with a dominant Doomben victory. Winning rider Moor sticks in the saddle and has won two from two over this sprint journey. Looks the one they all have to run down. LYLES (11) has only missed a drum once in six career outings and brings NSW formlines to the table. Keep very safe. BOSSED UP (8) got the job done over this course and distance at the latest effort and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside marble. Top-three credentials. BLUE SPINEL (10) rounds out the selections from the Gollan barn with Jones aboard.
